<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<title>항해99 미니 블로그 | 회원가입</title>
    <!-- AJAX 통신을 위한 jQuery -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Bulma CSS 링크 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.9.1/css/bulma.min.css">

    <!-- 커스텀 폰트 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard-dynamic-subset.css" />

    <!-- font-awesome 링크  -->
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/23b05056a7.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <style>
        *, input::placeholder, input, textarea{
            font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Segoe UI', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Noto Sans KR', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
        }

    </style>
    <script>
        function signUp(){
            let authorName = $('#authorName').val();
            let password = $('#password').val();
            let confirmPassword = $('#confirmPassword').val();
    
            if (authorName == '') {
                $('#authorName').focus()
                alert('닉네임을 입력하여 주세요.');
                return;
            } else if (password == '') {
                $('#password').focus()
                alert('암호를 입력하여 주세요.');
                return;
            } else if (confirmPassword == '') {
                $('#confirmPassword').focus()
                alert('암호 확인을 입력하여 주세요.');
                return;
            } else {
                // const data = {
                //         authorName: authorName,
                //         password: password,
                //         confirmPassword: confirmPassword,
                    // };
                $.ajax({
                    type: "POST",
                    url: "api/users",
                    // headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
                    data: {
                        authorName: authorName,
                        password: password,
                        confirmPassword: confirmPassword,
                    },
                    // JSON.stringify(data),
                    success: function (response) {
                        alert("회원가입을 축하드립니다!");
                        window.location.href = '/login';
                    },
                    error: function (error) {
                        alert("알 수 없는 오류입니다.");
                    },
                }); // else end
            } // 조건문 end
        }
    </script>
</head>


<body>
    <section class="hero is-info is-small">
        <div class="hero-body">
            <p class="title" style="text-align: center;">
            회원가입
            </p>
            <p class="subtitle" style="text-align: center;">
            항해99 블로그에서 나의 생각을 남겨보세요. 다른 사람과 의견을 나누세요.
            </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    <section class="hero is-halfheight">
		<div class="hero-body">
            <div class="container has-text-center">
				<div class="columns is-variable is-centered">
					<div class="column is-half has-text-left">
						<div class="field">
							<label class="label">아이디</label>
							<div class="control">
                                <input class="input is-medium" id="authorName" type="text" placeholder="로그인에 사용할 아이디를 입력하세요.">
							</div>
						</div>
                        <div class="field">
							<label class="label">비밀번호</label>
							<div class="control">
								<input class="input is-medium" id="password" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요.">
							</div>
						</div>
                        <div class="field">
							<label class="label">비밀번호 확인</label>
							<div class="control">
								<input class="input is-medium" id="confirmPassword" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 다시 한 번 입력하세요.">
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="control">
                                <div class="buttons is-centered">
                                    <button type="submit" class="button is-info is-medium" onclick="signUp();">
                                        <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i></span>
                                        <span>회원가입</span>
                                    </button>
                                    <button type="submit" class="button is-info is-outlined is-medium" onclick="window.location.href = '/login'">
                                        <span class="icon is-small"><i class="far fa-window-close"></i></span>
                                        <span>취소하기</span>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

</body>

</html>